title: Filipino Chicken and Noodles (Pancit)
ingredients: ['350g dried rice noodles', '1 teaspoon vegetable oil', '1 onion, finely diced', '3 cloves garlic, finely chopped', '280g diced cooked chicken breast meat', '1 small head cabbage, thinly sliced', '4 carrot, thinly sliced', '4 tablespoons soy sauce', '2 lemons, cut into wedges, for garnish']
